{
  "texts": [
    "For domain documentation (Fig. 3), the collaborators provided a manual that is used by LIEF POST end users and introduces most of the processes related to LIEF POST.",
    "We note that none of the TSs were exposed to RAGTAG, as part of the manual.",
    "We note that all the requirements, TS descriptions, and domain documentation collected in this stage were written in a mix of German and English.",
    "All the TSs were in English, with domain-or system-specific keywords in German.",
    "Most glossary terms were available to us as part of the domain documentation."
  ]
}